<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4632; padding: 2rem;">
  <% if @subscription.once_off? %>

    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Thanks for gooiing! ♻️</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      Hi <%= @subscription.user.first_name %>!
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Your once-off collection on <strong><%= @subscription.start_date.strftime("%-d %B") %></strong> is done.
      Every bag of kitchen scraps kept out of landfill is a real contribution to a greener Cape Town — thank you for giving it a go.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Alfred collected your scraps and they're on their way to compost, not a landfill somewhere under Table Mountain. That's the gooi way. 🌱
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      If you liked the experience, a weekly subscription means Alfred comes every <strong><%= @subscription.collection_day %></strong>
      and your kitchen scraps go straight to compost — no fuss, no trips, just one less thing to worry about.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <a href="<%= new_subscription_url %>"
         style="background-color: #FBB718; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        Start a Weekly Subscription
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Hope to see your kitchen scraps again soon 🍌🥬
    </p>

  <% else %>

    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Hi <%= @subscription.user.first_name %>! 👋</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      Your subscription (which started on <strong><%= @subscription.start_date.strftime('%e %b %Y') %></strong>) has run its course.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Over this time, we've collected <strong><%= @subscription.collections.where(skip: false).count %> times</strong>
      and picked up a total of <strong><%= @subscription.collected_volume_display %></strong> of compostables! ♻️
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      We've loved collecting your <strong>gooi-goodies</strong> — every bit of organic waste you diverted helped feed the soil and reduce landfill pressure.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      You're welcome to rejoin the movement anytime.
    </p>
    <p style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <a href="<%= new_subscription_url %>"
         style="background-color: #FBB718; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        Resubscribe Now
      </a>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      We hope to see you (and your kitchen scraps) again soon 👀🍌🥬
    </p>

  <% end %>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Thanks again,</p>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Kristen</p>
  <%= image_tag image_url('email-signature.png'), alt: "Kristen Kennedy email signature", style: "max-width: 250px; margin-top: 10px;" %>
</div>
